"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Ghosts and spirits said that the general old people will tell children, do not look for a mirror at night, because the mirror will look at the ghost, bad for their own.\\n\\n1. Superstitions say that looking in the mirror at night affects one's fortune and affects one's luck.\\n\\n3 timid said, because look in the mirror at night, will see his dark background behind, will feel afraid, so tell others not to look in the mirror at night. It's been passed on, with some scary embellishments, so many people are afraid to look in the mirror at night.\\n\\n1. Science says it's unscientific not to look in the mirror at night. Whether you look in the mirror at night is up to you.\\n\\nHow mirrors work: Why we can see ourselves in mirrors but not elsewhere. The reason for this is that the mirror is so smooth that particles of photons hitting the mirror regularly bounce back into our eyes (specular reflection) and therefore see themselves in the mirror. We can't send photons to ourselves from anywhere else because no other place provides a smooth surface for particles of photons, other surfaces just bounce off randomly (diffuse reflection) and therefore can't see ourselves.\",\"timestamp\":1638934631,\"title\":\"Reasons not to look in the mirror at night:\"},\"digest\":\"yYR74RiIFLwZ8lKkoIcT1YSaV_gE_nCTlqyH21zPRWM\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x870c780944bff123e9Bf1d60dc7F95eb4Ac4006E\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"TgMx3LTcwhnLZgfY0IKVQKqqK0zKeuL_f5peyaIA5-k\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"fl9aRYGaPGVt80rBJcMxZ6RoD7acCD2893aam5biHAU\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"h-k4XPI9Xqut4MYxrKhOoaShCyVDwKwaLqsE8rB67sYNA3dwPR3F1LSXl6OY5_0JNEX7rdi-tFXVU5pYmWPLfA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xa1f4e3e2bf9c6200fe25d7ae405c052e0ac7e096c801794f9b43173539bd4ef165222a93e034f5fe8eac8b3b0deef584b07788842a509cfa2c3a86e1a794cffd1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xy